🥋 “Life isn't about finding yourself. Life is about creating yourself.” 
🇯🇵 "頑張って" Kanji, (がんばって)Hiragana, (ガンバッテ)Katakana . "Gambatte.!!"
, “ganbatte” is often used as an expression to say “good luck”, “do not give up”, “do your best”, “hang in there”, or “keep going” to another person.
